{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T10:58:29.279Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Is Claude Code?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude Code is an agentic coding system"},{"type":"text","text":" that reads your entire codebase, plans multi-file changes, executes them using real development tools (edit files, run commands, tests), and delivers committed code — rather than just suggesting autocomplete lines."},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How It Works (The Agentic Loop)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"An agentic system acts toward a goal with autonomy, rather than responding to one prompt at a time. Claude Code follows this loop:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reads the codebase"},{"type":"text","text":"— starts with higher-level files, then dives deeper"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Plans a sequence of actions "},{"type":"text","text":"across multiple files"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Executes changes "},{"type":"text","text":"using real development tools (file editors, command runners, test frameworks)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluates the result"},{"type":"text","text":"— reads test errors, build failures"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Adjusts its approach "},{"type":"text","text":"and iterates on failures"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The developer sets the objective and retains control over what gets committed, but the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"execution loop runs independently"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key characteristics that define it:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it means"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agentic, not autocomplete"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Acts toward a goal with autonomy: reads codebase → plans actions → executes → evaluates → adjusts"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Project-level operation"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Understands your full codebase, git history, and how modules connect; works across multiple files simultaneously"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Terminal-first tool"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,